<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.8.8">
<l>eṉṉitu māyameṉ ṉappa ṉaṟintilaṉ</l>
<l>muṉṉaiya vaṇṇamē koṇṭaḷa vāyeṉṉa</l>
<l>maṉṉu namuciyai vāṉiṟ cuḻaṟṟiya</l>
<l>miṉṉu muṭiyaṉē yaccōvaccō</l>
<l rend="indent">vēṅkaṭa vāṇaṉē yaccōvaccō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He with the flashing crown</l>
<l>who whirled the persistent Namuśi into the sky</l>
<l>when [he] said, “What is this deception? My father did not know.</l>
<l rend="indent">Take [your] previous form [and] measure [the earth]!”</l>
<l>Oh! Oh! Resident of Vēṅkaṭam! Oh! Oh!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
